      <section class="section card">
        <h2>Our Services</h2>
        <p>
          At Core Crew Logistics, we provide comprehensive logistics solutions designed to keep your business moving forward. With a commitment to reliability, efficiency, and proactive communication, we serve clients across multiple industries, including retail, agriculture, manufacturing, and e-commerce. Our team manages every step of the supply chain, ensuring goods reach their destinations safely and on time.
        </p>
        <p>
          Whether you are a small business or a large enterprise, we tailor our services to fit your specific needs. Our use of advanced technology and our dedicated team members set us apart, allowing us to deliver exceptional value and peace of mind to our partners.
        </p>
      </section>
      <section class="section">
        <h3>What We Offer</h3>
        <div class="grid-3">
          <div class="card">
            <h4>Dispatch & Routing</h4>
            <p>Our experienced dispatch team uses real-time scheduling, GPS tracking, and route optimization to ensure your shipments move quickly and efficiently. We handle all the coordination so you can stay focused on your business.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h4>Warehousing</h4>
            <p>Our secure, well-managed warehouses provide storage, inventory management, and order fulfillment services. We use state-of-the-art systems to monitor stock levels, track shipments, and streamline pick-and-pack operations.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h4>Fleet & Drivers</h4>
            <p>We employ professional drivers and maintain a modern fleet of vehicles to ensure safe and timely deliveries. Our drivers are trained in safety, compliance, and customer service, representing your brand with professionalism on the road.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h4>Cargo & Freight Transportation</h4>
            <p>
              Core Crew Logistics specializes in the movement of all types of cargo and freight, from small parcels to large bulk shipments. We offer full truckload (FTL) and less-than-truckload (LTL) services, ensuring your goods are delivered precisely when and where you need them. Our freight experts handle route planning, carrier selection, and compliance documentation, taking the hassle out of your cargo management. Real-time tracking provides you with visibility at every stage, and our flexible solutions can accommodate even the most complex shipping requirements.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h4>Customer Support</h4>
            <p>Our responsive support team provides proactive updates and rapid solutions to any issues. We keep you informed every step of the way, with a focus on transparent communication and building long-term partnerships.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h4>Consulting</h4>
            <p>Our experts can assess your current logistics operations, identify areas for improvement, and provide actionable recommendations. From process optimization to supply chain analytics, we help you achieve greater efficiency and cost savings.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section class="section card">
        <h3>Why Choose Core Crew Logistics?</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Reliable Delivery:</strong> We pride ourselves on meeting deadlines and delivering your goods on time, every time.</li>
          <li><strong>End-to-End Cargo Solutions:</strong> We manage the safe, compliant, and efficient transport of your freight, whether by land, air, or sea.</li>
          <li><strong>Custom Solutions:</strong> No two businesses are alike. We develop logistics strategies that fit your unique needs.</li>
          <li><strong>Safety First:</strong> Our team follows strict safety protocols for every shipment and service.</li>
          <li><strong>Experienced Team:</strong> You benefit from decades of combined experience in logistics, transportation, and customer service.</li>
          <li><strong>Transparent Communication:</strong> We keep you informed with regular updates and clear reporting.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          Let us handle your logistics, so you can focus on growing your business. <a href="/contact">Contact us today</a> for a customized solution or to learn more about how Core Crew Logistics can support your operations.
        </p>
      </section>
      <section class="section card">
        <h3>Industries We Serve</h3>
        <p>
          Our cargo and freight services are trusted by clients in:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Agriculture – transporting produce, equipment, and supplies</li>
          <li>Manufacturing – moving raw materials and finished goods</li>
          <li>Retail & E-commerce – fast and reliable delivery for stores and online sellers</li>
          <li>Construction – shipping building materials and machinery</li>
          <li>Pharmaceuticals & Healthcare – safe and compliant delivery of sensitive goods</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          We understand the challenges unique to each industry and tailor our logistics solutions to meet your specific requirements.
        </p>
